            "call_id": "call_aff88c356bd2458e8d69de2f4e36b3a7",
            "output": "{\n        \"documents\": [\n          {\n            \"id\": \"856\",\n            \"content\": \"31) What is the temperature rating of the CozyNights Sleeping Bag? The CozyNights Sleeping Bag is rated for 3-season use and has a temperature rating of 20\\u00ef\\u00bf\\u00bdF to 60\\u00ef\\u00bf\\u00bdF (-6\\u00ef\\u00bf\\u00bdC to 15\\u00ef\\u00bf\\u00bdC). 32) Can the CozyNights Sleeping Bag be zipped together with another sleeping bag to create a double sleeping bag? Yes, two CozyNights Sleeping Bags can be zipped together to create a double sleeping bag, provided they have compatible zippers.\\nproduct_info_7.md\\nwww.microsoft.com\\nsleeping bag\\n\",\n            \"filepath\": \"\",\n            \"title\": \"product_info_7.md\",\n            \"url\": \"https://nirovinssearch-sweden.search.windows.net/\",\n            \"score\": 18.897884,\n            \"knowledgeSourceIndex\": 0\n          },\n          {\n            \"id\": \"854\",\n            \"content\": \"Review: I like the CozyNights Sleeping Bag, but I wish it came in more colors. The red color is nice, but I would prefer something more unique. Overall, it's a great sleeping bag. 35) Rating: 5\\nproduct_info_7.md\\nwww.microsoft.com\\nsleeping bag\\n\",\n            \"filepath\": \"\",\n            \"title\": \"product_info_7.md\",\n            \"url\": \"https://nirovinssearch-sweden.search.windows.net/\",\n            \"score\": 12.975415,\n            \"knowledgeSourceIndex\": 0\n          },\n          {\n            \"id\": \"852\",\n            \"content\": \"32) Rating: 4 Review: I bought the CozyNights Sleeping Bag, and while it's warm and lightweight, I wish it had a built-in pillow. Overall, it's a good sleeping bag for camping. 33) Rating: 5\\nproduct_info_7.md\\nwww.microsoft.com\\nsleeping bag\\n\",\n            \"filepath\": \"\",\n            \"title\": \"product_info_7.md\",\n            \"url\": \"https://nirovinssearch-sweden.search.windows.net/\",\n            \"score\": 12.254651,\n            \"knowledgeSourceIndex\": 0\n          },\n          {\n            \"id\": \"239\",\n            \"content\": \"Temperature Rating and Comfort: The MountainDream Sleeping Bag is rated for temperatures between 15\\u00c2\\u00b0F to 30\\u00c2\\u00b0F. However, personal comfort preferences may vary. It is recommended to use additional layers or adjust ventilation using the zipper and hood to achieve the desired temperature.\\nproduct_info_14.md\\nwww.microsoft.com\\nsleeping bag\\n\",\n            \"filepath\": \"\",\n            \"title\": \"product_info_14.md\",\n            \"url\": \"https://nirovinssearch-sweden.search.windows.net/\",\n            \"score\": 12.207125,\n            \"knowledgeSourceIndex\": 0\n          },\n          {\n            \"id\": \"831\",\n            \"content\": \"- Zipper Baffles: Yes - Footbox Design: Contoured - Zipper Compatibility: Can be zipped together with another sleeping bag ## CozyNights Sleeping Bag User Guide\\nproduct_info_7.md\\nwww.microsoft.com\\nsleeping bag\\n\",\n            \"filepath\": \"\",\n            \"title\": \"product_info_7.md\",\n            \"url\": \"https://nirovinssearch-sweden.search.windows.net/\",\n            \"score\": 11.551453,\n            \"knowledgeSourceIndex\": 0\n          }\n        ],\n        \"get_urls\": [\n          \"https://nirovinssearch-sweden.search.windows.net/indexes/sample_index/docs/856?api-version=2024-07-01&$select=embedId,token,title,url,category\",\n          \"https://nirovinssearch-sweden.search.windows.net/indexes/sample_index/docs/854?api-version=2024-07-01&$select=embedId,token,title,url,category\",\n          \"https://nirovinssearch-sweden.search.windows.net/indexes/sample_index/docs/852?api-version=2024-07-01&$select=embedId,token,title,url,category\",\n          \"https://nirovinssearch-sweden.search.windows.net/indexes/sample_index/docs/239?api-version=2024-07-01&$select=embedId,token,title,url,category\",\n          \"http